title: BridgePro 3.0.0.1 PC Game
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

An advanced, affordable, realistic contract rubber bridge
computer card game for Windows. For the beginner or the most
advanced player. Plays Standard American Yellow Card, Goren,
ACOL and Chicago style scoring. Various conventions can be
selected including: weak two bids, weak no-trump, splinter bids,
transfer bids, negative doubles, support doubles, help bid,
Jacoby 2NT response, inverted minors, Truscott 2NT response.

Version 3.0.0.1 features new bidding and card play algorithms,
vectorized card graphics, and Option to change the lead card
from enemy or partner&#039;s hand.
